{"tid":920991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李小加指若本港有獨特定位則不被邊緣化","createTime":"2018-11-29T08:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T14:10:47.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf61f6ac3a33708b464308b15903e18d386cc285","tid":920991,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:39:21.000Z","msg":"港交所(00388)行政總裁李小加表示, 巿場之間有互補作用同時, 亦存在競爭, 但認為中港三個交易所的競爭屬必然及健康, 有一定的競爭機制, 才能爭取更大的巿場份額, 因此交易所應有競爭精神.<br />\n        他認為, 交易所應注意定位, 清楚自己是巿場的服務者, 不可將自己變成市場, 相信本港只要有獨特定位便不會被邊緣化, 亦可從而產生新思維.<br />\n        他指, 每個交易所亦有不同使命, 以往較多內地及國際企業來港上市, 但亦有不少內地企業未能「走出去」, 並期望於內地上市的同時, 可得到海外資金參與交易, 因此出現滬港通及北向通, 令國際資金透過本港以進入內地市場, 同時亦提供機會將內地資金帶到本港進行配置, 但認為由於二級市場投資空間有限, 內地資金應流入一級市場, 相信新股通必須推出. 他又表示, 外界或會憂慮資金只往香港流, 但認為資金於不同市場之間流動的循環仍會持續.<br />\n        另外他表示, 港交所可推出指數, 容許指數成份股參與滬港通, 又指應由獨立第三方指數公司決定港股通標的, 而非港交所作決定."},{"pid":"344344dc5259da51348916c66c4ef1a7ea870521","tid":920991,"uid":28195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:08:40.000Z","msg":"李小加指若本<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港</span></span>有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">獨</span></span>特定位則不被邊緣化<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc56cb4eea7e05f559da853e7ef3ddd0933e95a","tid":920991,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"344344dc5259da51348916c66c4ef1a7ea870521","tid":920991,"uid":28195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:08:40.000Z","msg":"李小加指若本<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港</span></span>有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">獨</span></span>特定位則不被邊緣化<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22bcca82c58ba13a42ed09308c33c5ab78bd979","tid":920991,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5ba986d71ae3befafe6ed9d0c64a2b1fc3a120","tid":920991,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:10:47.000Z","msg":"要抑鬱了"}]}